title: #92Noon Live from TCO: Boudreau / Wobby / Caplan / Birk / M.Hughes
description:
The FAN's Paul Allen and Eric Nordquist talk the upcoming Winnipeg trip with Wild Head Coach Bruce Boudreau, then shift to Vikings and NFL conversations with Mike Wobschall, Adam Caplan, and Matt Birk.

In the final segment of the show, Vikings CB Mike Hughes joins to talk his road to recovery and recent performances.
